Pre requisite
-------
1. Java 9+ & Eclipse
2. TestNG
3. Maven(comes with Eclipse)

Dependencies
-------
rest assured
json-path
json
gson
testng
scribejava-apis
json-schema-validator
xml-schema-validator

Dependency site: mvnrepository.com
request response topic: reqres.in
https://app.reqres.in/playground
RestAssured: https://github.com/rest-assured/rest-assured/wiki/gettingstarted

http request
------
get
put
post
delete

Important - Import static packages

given - content type,cookies, add auth, add param, se headers info etc...
when - get,post,put,delete
then - validate status code, extract response, exact headers cookies & response body

